Syd hasn't wrestled for U/S since Season 5. In Season 5 she dominated, was undeafeated and took out Dia Zerva in the finals of Summer Vengeance to be crowned season 5 all round champion. At 5'2 and 118lbs she is pound for pound the most skilled wrestler on the roster. She ranked #1 in the lightweight and summer vengeance tournaments. She is currently the only active wrestler on the roster to have ever won a summer vengeance tournament.
Wenona missed season 9 but she's back and more tone and sexy than ever. She blasted her last opponent with a blow out victory. She has more mat time on the U/S than syd does. She's wrestled for 3 seasons longer than syd. Wenona is confident that her having more experience with U/S rules will definitely play its part in her victory today. BONUS OIL MATCH and a super sexy spanking. The winner of this match challenges the loser to a nude oil match with pins. If the loser can get the pin on the match winner, the loser will get to use the strap on on her.
